com.percussion.pso.effects
Class PSEffectLoggingEffect

java.lang.Object
  com.percussion.pso.effects.PSEffectLoggingEffect
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.percussion.extension.IPSExtension, com.percussion.relationship.IPSEffect
public class PSEffectLoggingEffect
extends Object
implements com.percussion.relationship.IPSEffect

Folder Follower Effect. Moves the dependent item into all of the folders occupied by the owner item, and removes it from any other folders. Operates only at relationship construction time. At all other times, the item is not moved.

Author:
DavidBenua Copyright 2007, Percussion Software, Inc.

m_codeRoot

private ThreadLocal m_codeRoot
This holds the 'root' directory for this extension. When installed, all files are installed relative to this location. Files can be loaded from anywhere under this directory and no where else (by default, the actual security policy may vary). This object could be used to load a property file when executing the Effect. Initialized in {#link init(IPSExtensionDef, File)}, never changed or null after that.
